company_name: FEINKOSTFABRIK GUSTAV L. LANGBEIN & CO. GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG
information: The company FEINKOSTFABRIK GUSTAV L. LANGBEIN & CO. GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1959, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Freshwater crayfish industries. It is based in Hamburg, Germany.
